01:49.240 --> 01:52.575
[ calliope plays Chopin's "Funeral march" ]

01:58.484 --> 02:03.031
No! No-o-o-o!
[ Crying ]

02:03.032 --> 02:05.305
<i>No. Get off me!</i>

02:05.307 --> 02:11.227
- Hold up. I think we've got an elemental.
