02:23.979 --> 02:25.325
- You again?
- Because that meeting ...

02:25.327 --> 02:28.544
Good god, man. Have you no
humanity left in you whatsoever?

02:28.546 --> 02:34.167
This is why you have no friends,
Vendata. [ Camera shutter clicks ]

02:34.788 --> 02:37.648
<i><font color="cyan"> sync & correction by f1nc0
~ addic7ed.com ~ </font> </i>

