04:13.017 --> 04:17.069
[ Robotic voice ] I am glad to be of
assistance. We are all on the same team, right?

04:17.071 --> 04:22.725
<i>And teamwork is what it's all about, so
it is with great pleasure that I officially</i>

04:22.727 --> 04:28.337
<i>introduce the new Councilman 4 to our little family.</i>

04:29.083 --> 04:33.068
<i>- Thanks, guys. Really looking forward ...
- So, if there's no other business, I hereby</i>

04:33.070 --> 04:38.541
<i>- adjourn this session of the council of 13.
